000
OCTAVIA TEA
WINTER MINT
CAFFEINE-FREE RED TEA
One of our best-selling teas, Winter-
Mint blends Rooibos, sweet vanilla
& a touch of chocolate-mint into a
soothing treat & healthy alternative
to dessert. Also called Red Tea,
Rooibos is rich in antioxidants &
anti-aging properties.
TO ORDER:
I866) 506-6387
